{"tid":934841,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★沈振盈：港股最壞情況恐怕仍未出現","createTime":"2018-12-09T14:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T15:10:43.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"02dd5cc47d8cf51e536d0449580e43979b42104c","tid":934841,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T14:50:59.000Z","msg":"訊匯證券行政總裁沈振盈在東方產經「另類指標」專欄表示，港股繼續着急升急跌的走勢，去周初藉中美首腦會面的消息而挾上，引來了不少投資者高追，亦挾死了淡倉。<br />\n<br />\n然而，此消息其實一早已是預期之內，亦並非甚麼大好消息，只是因為媒體的渲染，配合大戶挾上的行動，就輕易令到市場以為，中美雙方可以和解。若被市場情緒牽引而追貨，結果當然是中伏。<br />\n<br />\n很明顯，美國發動貿易戰的動機，根本不在於「貿易」的不平衡，而是另有所圖。中國的底線，也明白不過，就是要在資訊科技領域超越美國，取得領導權。若美方一意孤行，根本雙方是沒有可能可以達成協議。<br />\n<br />\n至於在宏觀因素方面，經濟要下行是不爭的事實，在美國持續縮表之下，資金憂慮經濟衰退而作部署，導致債券孳息曲線倒掛，因而引發美股大跌。其實一切皆在基本分析所預計之內，只是市場太過盲目地樂觀而已。戊戌年尚餘不足兩個月，香港股民宜縛穩安全帶，最壞的情況仍未出現。<br />\n<br />\n本周每日的股市走勢預測：<br />\n周一(丙子日)：天干屬火地支屬水，水火交戰之局，走勢反覆。<br />\n周二(丁丑日)：天干屬火地支屬土，火生土之局，顯著反彈。<br />\n周三(戊寅日)：天干屬土地支屬木，木剋土之局，市況震盪，反覆回落。<br />\n周四(己卯日)：天干屬土地支屬木，木剋土之局，持續弱勢。<br />\n周五(庚辰日)：天干屬金地支屬土，土生金之局，低位反彈。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181209/bkn-20181209213303452-1209_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181209%2Fbkn-20181209213303452-1209_00842_001.html&d=es%2BtSAvE9Ha4YFt1qxhR2f9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=b7968dff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181209/bkn-20181209213303452-1209_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1770f4d9635566bf066370a19f8de2f83693295a","tid":934841,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T14:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/11/192622_4ddec4f8a5faaf54ba5e5e73d6a5d390.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2F192622_4ddec4f8a5faaf54ba5e5e73d6a5d390.png&h=5b3b95a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1a9eaa79e8fb67f4eec3a5b68559fc4c99dbbc4","tid":934841,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T14:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/11/192623_ae5b8f2042961914167603a5d4bcf20b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2F192623_ae5b8f2042961914167603a5d4bcf20b.png&h=899b903b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f05669fea241f5fdceaa0349b1215741904838f5","tid":934841,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T14:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97bd0bd288ef4d2637ce99e87e4c1b3ea2623f38","tid":934841,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T14:58:51.000Z","msg":"即係最壞時期過咗 牛一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e238e6d06f1ab9db4251b45653a121f049bfff3","tid":934841,"uid":204803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T14:59:07.000Z","msg":"唔覺得大陸同美國可以和解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等大跌執平貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"083cd3bb922e1a5520c4043af767cb988f0aba52","tid":934841,"uid":208159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T15:02:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54b122cccfcc4d94df3757e22aab7622df7d4dda","tid":934841,"uid":131078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T15:05:35.000Z","msg":"最尾嗰張<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386487bd50e0d79d57adaeb7dff6ef6daffd2629","tid":934841,"uid":6297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e238e6d06f1ab9